{"tid":1764864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【代fd轉發】【最新一輪Deadline已過！偽善慈善機構 對警暴冷眼旁觀 2/12升級行動即時展開！！】","createTime":"2019-12-01T12:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T15:42:17.000Z","uid":97327,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"30a1ba451d74b8480c837cfc5bb9f3682e33f62f","tid":1764864,"uid":97327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:15:15.000Z","msg":"自從上次無國界醫生對poly手足單野，相信大家都睇到所謂「慈善機構」係幾咁係偽善！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但仆街嘅慈善機構，又點止無國界醫生一間，香港咁多間國際級慈善機構，每年吸香港人嘅善款超過20億，滿口仁義道德嘅國際組織！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但自612以嚟絕大部分因為怕得罪藍絲donor、藍絲最高層，眼見暴警多次使用過度武力，違反機構理念，包括醫療道德、兒童權利，人道主義等行為，居然視若無睹！<br />\n<br />\n自6月到宜家，除左紅十字會有實際行動之外，以下機構依然未有伸出援手：<br />\n<br />\n1. 宣明會（2018善款超9.1億）：出左個垃圾聲明，以後大家祈完禱當捐左<br />\n2. 無國界醫生（2017總收入超5億）：係香港只做捐款，垃圾中嘅垃圾<br />\n3. 樂施會（2017總收入超2.5億）：無回應，平行時空！！！<br />\n4. 奧比斯香港（2018年總收入超2.1億）：無回應，平行時空！！！<br />\n5. UNICEF HK（2017年總收入超1.7億）：無回應，平行時空！！！<br />\n6. Save the Children （2017年總收入超1.6億）：無回應，平行時空！！！<br />\n7. 國際培幼會（2017年總收入近8000萬）：無回應，平行時空！！！<br />\n<br />\n1/12 12:00死線已過，但各大INGO依然龜縮！所以升級行動正式展開！！<br />\n<br />\n升級行動如下 ：<br />\n1. 根據以下時間表，手足10:00am直接踩上以上7間INGO Office表達訴求，係門口整連儂牆，直接向各大INGO高層表達訴求：<br />\n<br />\n2/12 (Mon)：樂施會、國際培幼會<br />\n3/12 (Tue)：無國界醫生、Save The Children<br />\n4/12 (Wed)：UNICEF HK<br />\n5/12 (Thu)：宣明會<br />\n6/12 (Fri)：奧比斯香港<br />\n<br />\n2. 全民轟炸INGO總部Facebook投訴機構忽視香港人權問題<br />\n<br />\n附上各大INGO地址及總部Facebook：<br />\n<br />\n1.宣明會 - 香港九龍大角咀晏架街四號麗華中心二樓 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WorldVisionInternational/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWorldVisionInternational%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=895f045e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WorldVisionInternational/</a><br />\n2.無國界醫生 - 香港西環德輔道西410 至 418 號太平洋廣場22樓 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/msf.english/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmsf.english%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=80f5ff53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/msf.english/</a><br />\n3.樂施會 - 香港北角馬寶道28號華匯中心17樓<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Oxfam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FOxfam%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=42c02cc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Oxfam/</a><br />\n4. 奧比斯香港 - 九龍觀塘鴻圖道21號訊科中心5樓C室 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/OrbisInternational/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FOrbisInternational%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=669fa9ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/OrbisInternational/</a><br />\n5.UNICEF HK  - 香港英皇道75-83號聯合出版大廈7樓<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/unicef/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funicef%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=e2224522\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/unicef/</a><br />\n6. Save the Children - 西環德輔道西410-418號太平洋廣場8樓 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/savethechildrenuk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsavethechildrenuk%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=48279572\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/savethechildrenuk/</a><br />\n7. 國際培幼會 - 香港筲箕灣興民街68號海天廣場201室 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/planinternational/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplaninternational%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=ceea9ae5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/planinternational/</a><br />\n<br />\n為左所有已死去嘅手足，我地要用行動令呢D滿口仁義道德嘅機構出手譴責警暴、譴責政府，甚至幫手向國際求救為止！<br />\n<br />\n一位於慈善機構工作，對公司所作所為睇唔過眼嘅香港人 上"},{"pid":"ee15562b966d873179a6b8465cfb9a680d3be8ff","tid":1764864,"uid":271516,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"自從知道所謂管理層一年收入之後<br />\n已經無再捐過任何錢"},{"pid":"3837df426aa0778d22fbc382612817159593fdce","tid":1764864,"uid":97327,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ee15562b966d873179a6b8465cfb9a680d3be8ff","tid":1764864,"uid":271516,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"自從知道所謂管理層一年收入之後<br />\n已經無再捐過任何錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:22:29.000Z","msg":"喺 捐畀手足好過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d940e8053bea148c9a92c59afe35b30b239bc98d","tid":1764864,"uid":267793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:37:19.000Z","msg":"有用post 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d57b826989c4580be8eebf3f824bff92408051","tid":1764864,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:46:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f26eda98a260e320a896a8ed95e001a4396c78b2","tid":1764864,"uid":41159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1784d8a71313b23d8393be126057b8933c497f57","tid":1764864,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee15562b966d873179a6b8465cfb9a680d3be8ff","tid":1764864,"uid":271516,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"自從知道所謂管理層一年收入之後<br />\n已經無再捐過任何錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:57:15.000Z","msg":"[手續費]<br />\n高過2成既都係垃圾"},{"pid":"e6c8c8e0ea71d453d990aab62dfe4296a059204d","tid":1764864,"uid":34423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44fe3358ea16fd326eea9cf21bd3e9532ebaa0a","tid":1764864,"uid":67896,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":